long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This extension is used to change the colours of the turn in button (in a google doc from google classroom), and to also create support for the turn in button on google slides. You can customize the turn in button to be whatever colour you want, and also minimize/maximize the options menu.

This extension is open source on GitHub! View and download the code here : https://github.com/codingtuba/turnin/tree/master
